<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>8: There were four 2s so I counted by 2 four times like 2, 4, 6, 8.</li>
      <li>16: I knew that 4 twos was 8 and now there are two groups of 8, so I doubled 8 to get 16.</li>
      <li>20: I knew that 2 fives is 10 and there are 4 fives, so I doubled 10.</li>
      <li>40: I knew that four fives was 20 and now there are 2 groups of 20, so I doubled 20 to get 40.</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


