  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="narrative-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>The purpose of this Number Talk is to elicit strategies students have for counting by 2 and 5. These understandings help students develop fluency and will be used later in this lesson when students will need to be able to scale bar graphs.</p>
<p>When students notice the number of equal addends are doubled in the second expression, they are looking for and making sense of structure (MP7). When they notice the pattern repeats in the second pair of expressions and use the pattern to find the value of the sum, they are also looking for and expressing regularity in repeated reasoning (MP8).</p>
